How Speech Generation Works

When you say:

Speech cyber warfare and international security

Drogon will:

Send the topic to OpenAI.
Ask for a 90-second MUN opening speech.
Display the speech in the terminal.
Save it as:
speech.txt

inside the Drogon-AI folder.

You can open that file later and copy the speech for your conference.

Troubleshooting
Microphone Not Working

Check:

Windows Settings → System → Sound → Input
Make sure the correct microphone is selected.
Increase input volume to 80–100%.
"OpenAI API key not found"

Run:

setx OPENAI_API_KEY "your_key_here"

Then restart Command Prompt.

PyAudio Installation Error

Use Python 3.12 and run:

py -3.12 -m pip install pyaudio
Voice Recognition Mishears Words

Speak clearly and keep the microphone about 15–20 cm from your mouth.

